{\*\generator Msftedit 5.41.15.1515;}\viewkind4\uc1\pard\cf1\b\f0\fs20 The \cf2 Main Data Source\cf1  of a task is set in the first line of the Data View tab, as you can see by looking at the source code for this program.\par
\par
The Main Data Source is the one that set the number of records that will be displayed in given Data View. If there are 100 records in the data source, and no filtering criteria, then 100 records can be shown in the Data View. Other Data Sources may be selected, but there will only be one record selected for each record in the Main Data Source.\par
